Genre - Class in Unnamed Package
Genre is the class which contains all the values for the columns of the Genre table These values are retrieved through a series of methods in the Parsers Class, and they are also inputted to the actual database using methods in the PopulateDB class
Genre(String) - Constructor for class Genre
Creates the genre object, which stores a name.
genreParser(File) - Method in class Parsers
This custom parser checks for a specific set of key-value pairs that match the different columns that are in the Genre table.
